@startuml
title Use Case: Report Incident

actor "Citizen" as C
actor "Dispatcher" as D
actor "Officer" as O

usecase "Report Incident" as UC

C --> UC : reports incident
D --> UC : processes report
O --> UC : responds to incident

UC .> (Verify Location) : include
UC .> (Determine Priority) : include
UC .> (Create Record) : include

UC <.. (Emergency Response) : extend <<if emergency>>
UC <.. (Multi-Unit Dispatch) : extend <<if major incident>>
UC <.. (Medical Assistance) : extend <<if injuries>>

note right of UC
  Citizen reports crime or emergency
  Dispatcher processes and dispatches
  Officer responds to the incident
end note
@enduml
